text.tspan: Share of deaths from suicide, 1990 to 2019
Suicide deaths are underreported in many countries due to social stigma and cultural or legal concerns. This data
is adjusted for this underreporting to estimate the actual number of suicides.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
